Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:24:02.16,ED-JP-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}ワガママでもいいですか?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:05.81,ED-JP-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}許してくれますか?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:09.61,ED-JP-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}あなたのこと少しだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:13.20,ED-JP-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}「キライ」になってみたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:20.23,ED-JP-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}困った顔をして 苦笑いするかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:27.75,ED-JP-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}それでも やってやれないことはないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:29.73,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,0)\blur7.5}ステキになりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.73,0:24:31.31,ED-JP-Color3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)\blur7.5}ステキになりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:35.23,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}センチメンタル吹き飛ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:36.82,ED-JP-Color4,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,0)\blur7.5}あなたを 守るための 強さになりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.82,0:24:38.61,ED-JP-Color5,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}あなたを 守るための 強さになりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.61,0:24:42.89,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)\blur7.5}あなたを 守るための 強さになりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:46.97,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}I know you. You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.97,0:24:51.89,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}いつでも やさしい笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.03,0:24:55.13,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}独り占めしたくなるの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.13,0:24:58.76,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}期待してしまうんです
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:01.51,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}ね、だから
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.51,0:25:06.52,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}はじまりの恋にしたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:08.27,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}好きなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.27,0:25:11.56,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}ちょっぴり手前で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.77,0:25:16.84,ED-JP-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}あなたを監視つめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:24:02.16,ED-CH-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}我可以任性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:05.81,ED-CH-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}你会原谅我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:09.61,ED-CH-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}对于你的事稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:13.20,ED-CH-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}「讨厌」了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:20.23,ED-CH-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}你会露出因困扰而苦笑的样子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:27.75,ED-CH-Color1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}不过即使那样 你也不会抛下我的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:29.73,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,0)\blur7.5}想要变得 更加完美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.73,0:24:31.31,ED-CH-Color3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)\blur7.5}想要变得 更加完美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:35.23,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}把所有悲伤的心情全部吹走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:36.82,ED-CH-Color4,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,0)\blur7.5}想要有能够守护你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.82,0:24:38.61,ED-CH-Color5,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想要有能够守护你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.61,0:24:42.89,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,100)\blur7.5}想要有能够守护你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:46.97,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}I know you. You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.97,0:24:51.89,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}无论何时你温柔的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.03,0:24:55.13,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}我都想要独自占有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.13,0:24:58.76,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}不禁如此期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:01.51,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}呐 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.51,0:25:06.52,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}想让这成为我恋爱的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:08.27,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}最喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.27,0:25:11.56,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.77,0:25:16.84,ED-CH-Color2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)\blur7.5}时刻都注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------TXT---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,学长 不能偷看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,才不会看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在战斗开始前好好休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 亚拉道尔那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 你要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你说要吃什么 姬柊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 是饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,应急的干粮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,话说学长你刚才想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 学长真是个下流的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在南宫老师家时 稍微空出了一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 和情人节绝对没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好的好的 怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 姬柊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,本飞艇遭到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,全员 进入一级警戒状态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,动作真快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,完成补给吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我吃饱…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 不是你想的那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,话说这真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(302,330)}Nalakuvera
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是纳拉克维勒的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:03:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,浅葱那家伙 是动真格杀了我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,阁下 高度无法继续维持
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去要坠机了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,全员 准备稳住迫降的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经到达目的地上空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 速速出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,330)}Natra Cinereus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,甲壳的银雾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,浅葱也好 你也好 怎么都爱乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,晓古城 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是…瓦托拉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我来来对付他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,「夜枭」遭到击坠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,圣护结界 输出功率下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去 十分钟也撑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,准备启动空间转移室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(304,330)}Nalakuvera
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,转移目标为纳拉克维勒的操纵者潜伏处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,等…这也太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,纱矢华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你有认真愿意和古城结合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这时候你突然问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为在这个时候才要问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 纱矢华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这场战争目的 是为了让晓古城成为夜之帝国的王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须召集优秀的血之随从
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,换句话说 就是组建后宫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你没有成为其中一员的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不能让你置身事内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我…又没想过成为晓古城的伴侣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,空间转移室 准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要一起走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能和雪菜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,管它什么后宫不后宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 有你这句话就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,传送后「蓓兹薇德」在上空待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,将精灵炉的功率分配到圣护结界上也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,开始传送
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,男友大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在下也是遵守规则 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,又不能用眷兽破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,动手 亚丝塔露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,330)}Accept
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接受命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(266,330)}Execute
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(344,330)}Rhododaktylos
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,执行  蔷薇的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小那月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是来帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是来帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的小丫头的班主任是我的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,开心点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,特别的惩罚等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等等是也 老师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请大发慈悲 至少以武士的怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这子弹…是圣歼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,浅葱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我来阻止蓝羽学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,学长趁这个机会去阿尔缇阿鲁公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 姬柊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,圣域条约非加盟国的代表们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎勉强还有一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦托拉那家伙 到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:07:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一听到要与第四真祖为敌就立刻软了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对与这些逃兵 我施加了惩罚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,玷污圣战的胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这模样很适合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小那月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你把代表们送到医院去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我来揍扁他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(362,330)}Regulus Aurum
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,速速出现 狮子的黄金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,跋难陀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 就像在做梦一样 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样和你战斗感觉太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,来 让你见识我的全新力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这股力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,圣歼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,330)}Mesarthim Adamas
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,神羊的金刚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会就这样永别了吗 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,葛莲妲 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(280,330)}Freikugel plus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,六式降魔弓·改 全力齐射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝羽学姐 请停手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不进行战争 也能拯救弦神岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只要晓学长打败阿尔缇阿鲁公就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那样就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,古城以第四真祖的身份统治弦神岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,之后他又会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还能回到普通的高中生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,剥夺了那家伙的归宿却只救弦神岛 根本没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要夺走古城的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,无论学长是第四真祖还是夜之帝国的王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会守护学长的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是我监视者的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你那翅膀是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱就能这么任性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱是蓝羽学姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,长得漂亮 身材又好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,晓学长总是依赖你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,古城依赖的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我不清楚监视者什么名堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你们总是在一起卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝羽学姐才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,上课时 午休时 不也一直跟他黏在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,再说 古城还没送过我戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是狮子王机关的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,和蓝羽学姐的耳环不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但这戒指是古城给你戴上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝羽学姐才是 平时都可以直呼晓学长的名字不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你会介意这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,葛莲妲 葛莲妲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,古城君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,古城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是圣歼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那个魔法阵 是斐川学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她说在古城君恢复之前 由她来吸引敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就一个人去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝羽学姐 晓学长就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,古城 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,浅…浅葱？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你快睁开眼睛啊 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么又 我又没在你面前哭过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你这人真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么到现在都还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,浅…浅葱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不太明白这种事该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏都快要跳出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 浅葱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,突然做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你吸我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是你的话 我就不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,浅葱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽量温柔一点 但一开始或许会疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我会忍的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,随你怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs30\bord0\shad0\fn方正小标宋_GBK\pos(320,270)\c&HE3E3E3&}真祖大战篇Ⅳ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,斐川学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你那对翅膀怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,说来话长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,煌坂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拉·法莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦托拉的眷兽突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呦 浅葱 你看上去清爽不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别贫嘴了 我很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,关于瓦托拉眷兽消失的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,几分钟之前 弦神岛周边的龙脉被截断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在圣歼的威力应该已经大打折扣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你说截断龙脉 这种事能办得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我就是为此而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,古城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,结瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我让利维坦张开最大限度的魔力障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,正阻断着龙脉的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 结瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮上哥哥的忙 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但就算是利维坦也撑不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,30分钟就是极限
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在此期间快想办法解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,30分钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,时间太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,学长 你恢复意识了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,伤势如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拉·法莉娅和煌坂也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,正好 关于瓦托拉眷兽消失的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在由利维坦阻断龙脉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是时间有限
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只有30分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 都怪我一再碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 你不也是为了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 浅葱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊 古城就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才你把交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不能断言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但应该只有这把枪能确实打倒瓦托拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 晓古城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会做好婚礼的准备 等你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,若无其事地说这个 太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好了 你们两个一定要平安回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,回到我们的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 到最后还得让你陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今还说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,之前被卷入很多事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你还对我做了那么多事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说的我跟犯罪似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但不管到去哪或是做什么 我都会跟你去天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我可是学长的监视者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我等得不耐烦了 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 第四真祖打倒该隐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,获得圣歼之力的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这舞台很适合与你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,第四真祖杀害该隐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为天部下的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,330)}Root
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,被称为原初的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是天部惧怕本用于监视咎神的第四真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,反而成为其盟友而设下的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,第四真祖亲手杀了该隐 而陷入了绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,背叛了自己的创造者天部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但他最终同样失败 落得被分为十二个部封印的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个绝望的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒未必
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奥萝菈还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(262,330)}Hektos
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,「第六」和凪沙救了她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧 瓦托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,该隐并不希望变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 该隐为了打倒天部而创造的圣歼的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你无法使用它的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我正全力与你战斗 这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,难陀 跋难陀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍受了这么久的无聊 早就不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的历史不断上演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,世界的风景一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有全力抵抗恐怖作出的斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,才能治愈我的无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让我见识下生命消逝时所散发的光辉吧 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,330)}Regulus Aurum
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,狮子的黄金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你真可悲 瓦托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在畏惧什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你和小孩子毫无区别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不开心就胡乱耍发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不去尝试创造让自己忘却无聊的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只顾追求一时的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,别以为你能一直任性下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的话很新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是第一个对我这么说话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经夺不走任何东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你企图毁灭的世界 就由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始 就是我的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你错了 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(358,330)}圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真愉快啊 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这绝美的战斗 再多让我见识一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,原初之蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,何等强大的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我能打倒这样的对手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,回想起来 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(270,330)}Kaleido Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,焰光夜伯之血统的继承者 晓古城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,解放汝之枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现身吧 第八号眷兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,330)}Shaula Viola
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,蝎虎的紫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,竟如此抵抗原初之蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我心爱的第四真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(196,330)}Hektos
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,「第六」托付给我的眷兽 现在交还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,姬柊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕一次也好 请学长叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就像叫凪沙 蓝羽学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还有奥萝菈那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 雪菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,速速出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,330)}Minelauva Iris
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,冥姬的虹炎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,330)}Kiffa Ater
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,夜摩的黑剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,晓古城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,变身能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你的王牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你要与我合为一体 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会成为新的第四真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 瓦托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,狮子神子 高神剑巫 诚心祷祝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,破魔曙光 雪霞神狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,以钢之神威
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了 瓦托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,助我讨尽恶神百鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不给我最后一击吗 古城
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没恨你到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真遗憾 如果对象是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒觉得被吞噬也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我为这一连串的无力之举道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,第四真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢您实现阁下的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,异境侵蚀？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦托拉 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本就打算在输给你之后这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咎神该隐遭到流放后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也是他从之得到圣歼智慧的异次元地球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,到底会遇到怎样的敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看来 短时间内是不会无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,古城 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,圣域条约机构发出通知
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,弦神岛的大规模破坏魔具认定被撤回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且并正式承认第四真祖的领地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是新的夜之帝国了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快点回来吧 我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧 姬柊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 姬柊小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,学长是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.94,0:25:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.38,0:25:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要烤熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.26,0:25:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,化成灰了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.60,0:25:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 我好歹也是夜之帝国的王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.48,0:25:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.02,0:25:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么我还要在这里些春假作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.90,0:25:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是吸血鬼真祖该做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.46,0:25:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,学长 别光抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.36,0:25:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就真的要陪我和凪沙读同一个年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.56,0:25:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这座城市 被称作弦神岛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.06,0:25:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,它漂浮于太平洋之上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.08,0:26:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,由碳塑纤维  树脂  金属  经魔术建造而成的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.16,0:26:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在这座岛上 有一位少年
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.68,0:26:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,第四真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.44,0:26:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,本该是不存在的第四位真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.98,0:26:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小那月老师发来紧急委托
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.90,0:26:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在人工岛北区B层的研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.22,0:26:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有魔导生命体逃跑了
